        "description": "<p>Adds a &#8220;nonce&#8221; field to the comments form.  If the &#8220;nonce&#8221; is missing on submit, the comment will return an error.<br />\nThis will stop submissions from remote sites and cut down of the comments received from comment bots</p>\n",
